          }
        },
        "text_EUj39w": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Jasion offers electric bikes for adults—built for the rides people actually take, from commuting and errands to campus trips and weekend exploring. Choose a folding e-bike for easy storage, or a fat-tire option for trails and rougher roads, and enjoy a smooth, confidence-inspiring ride that helps you go farther with less effort.</p>",
